column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, s.specobjid, p.ra, p.dec, p.type, s.class, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r, p.expRad_r, p.expRadErr_r, s.z, g.bptclass, g.lgm_tot_p5#, z.spiral, z.elliptical, z.uncertain FROM photoobj as p JOIN SpecObj as s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN galSpecExtra as g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE type = # and class = &&& &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
